surface area, and requiring NO additional power.  Is this correct?  I
went by the rules on page 66.

Armor:			0.01732		0.12124		----
6.062
     --TL7 Comp Lam
     --rating on Head/Chest =3D 7 (1.0cm)
     --rating on Arms/Legs =3D 6 (0.73cm)
