    'body' => '> At 02:40 PM 9/20/97 -0800, Peter Newman <pnewman@alaska.net> wrote:
> >Ethan Henry wrote<egh@klg.com>
> >> Also, the idea that someone with Gunenry-3 and Computer-3 can sit
